casebody.data:
April 27, 1964. No. 1014,

Misc.

Krepel v. Heinze, Warden. Petitioner pro se. Stanley Mosk, Attorney General of California, and Doris H. Maier, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
